des:
Use the app or voice control to tell your smart devices how to behave. Increase light, change colors, turn on and off and much more. SiGN Smart Home comes with a variety of different smart home products. 

After connecting Alexa to your SiGN Smart Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "SiGN Smart Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one SiGN Smart Home account in our "SiGN Smart Home" app;
(3). You need to have some SiGN Smart Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "SiGN Smart Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "SiGN Smart Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "SiGN Smart Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "SiGN Smart Home", and you'll be navigated to SiGN Smart Home login page;
(9). Input your SiGN Smart Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
